Ecommerce is buying and selling that is conducted in an online environment, through an ecommerce website. An application is a software program designed to accomplish one or more tasks in a particular software environment. An ecommerce application is a software application that is specifically designed to support the creation of an ecommerce website or add functionality to it.

This is an ecommerce application built using the MERN stack, which includes MongoDB, Express, React, and Node.js. The application provides users with the ability to browse and purchase products online.

This is an ecommerce application built using the Ionic-Angular stack, which includes Ionic and Angular. The application provides users with the ability to browse and purchase products on their mobile devices.
